-    /// Tests if two statements can be considered equal
-    ///
-    /// Statements can be trivially equal if the kinds match.
-    /// But they can also be considered equal in the following case A:
-    /// ```ignore (MIR)
-    /// discriminant(_0) = 0;   // bb1
-    /// _0 = move _1;           // bb2
-    /// ```
